{
  "stem": "1799.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are the Germans, SS?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said they had been gone for four days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Was he speaking to you in English?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was speaking to me in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I understood English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- as I walked up to him, the first-- the first of my senses that reacted was his aftershave lotion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had not really smelled any aftershave lotion in a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And It was kind of unusual that that would be a symbolic reaction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, this officer, he was a young man, said, where are the rest of the inmates?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I showed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He walked with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he saw they were, you know, dozens of-- of corpses, cadavers, and maybe 20 or 30 or 40 people that he saw that were barely moving around.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were maybe only eight people that were able to move like myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to his driver to call his headquarters to set up a set of guards around the camp to quarantine it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was pretty obvious to him with all the cadavers and-- and other people sick that a typhus or any other kind of sickness would be rampant, or would become rampant, which was then set up that same day.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before the American guards were stationed in place, I walked out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That same day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It all happen on May 1.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember that I figured, why should I wait for formalities or any of that?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was feeling pretty good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had had some potatoes in me, and I'd had some water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I climbed-- the camp had kind of a-- a-- a series of-- of earth mounds around it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
